  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Alchemist with a fatal illness. You traveled to a hidden valley where you hope to find a cure. A dark story with alchemy, exploration and light-deck building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.poster.avif?t=1740150942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.webm?t=1740150942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.mp4?t=1740150942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Improve your Actions through Deck Building:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cards from <strong>THREE</strong> different decks to explore, gather herbs, rest and create potions. Build your decks by adding Passive, Action or Alchemy cards, or replace existing cards to help you in your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/e6f8fb46527500480f10519774b24306.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build the World through Exploration:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world grows through your actions. Place lakes, fields, and forests while exploring, each containing herbs to help you in crafting potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/6dd0c293c40bf41821bac9605280be02.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft cures and potions through Alchemy:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While your herbs are the ingredients, your Alchemy cards are powerful tools to modify them. Create a variety of potions to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/4812472e2382baabe42b9eacc3e7b8ff.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But things are rarely as simple as they seem. Dangers are roaming around. Avoid them while trying to explore all the ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Alchemist with a fatal illness. You traveled to a hidden valley where you hope to find a cure. A dark story with alchemy, exploration and light-deck building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.poster.avif?t=1740150942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.webm?t=1740150942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/22db3b757c0a8b83c45f8eca3c3a101b.mp4?t=1740150942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Improve your Actions through Deck Building:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cards from <strong>THREE</strong> different decks to explore, gather herbs, rest and create potions. Build your decks by adding Passive, Action or Alchemy cards, or replace existing cards to help you in your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/e6f8fb46527500480f10519774b24306.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build the World through Exploration:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world grows through your actions. Place lakes, fields, and forests while exploring, each containing herbs to help you in crafting potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/6dd0c293c40bf41821bac9605280be02.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft cures and potions through Alchemy:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While your herbs are the ingredients, your Alchemy cards are powerful tools to modify them. Create a variety of potions to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365370/extras/4812472e2382baabe42b9eacc3e7b8ff.avif?t=1740150942\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But things are rarely as simple as they seem. Dangers are roaming around. Avoid them while trying to explore all the ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
